{"id": "ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE", "rating": 4.7, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_INEXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 778, "displayName": {"text": "La Perla #3", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Old-school, unadorned counter serve selling tacos, burritos & other Mexican street-food classics.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aSlRIWnFXVUZCTlVWbWRYSldNbHBTVkZKME0wRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’ve got a burrito here that was great. The line was super long. Seems like a popular place. Know what you want before you reach the front of the line. The food was good. I will come back if the line wasn’t as long. Seems like people get food here and then go to the ocean. Ask for what salsa you want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’ve got a burrito here that was great. The line was super long. Seems like a popular place. Know what you want before you reach the front of the line. The food was good. I will come back if the line wasn’t as long. Seems like people get food here and then go to the ocean. Ask for what salsa you want.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Juma Nyumba", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102723974633784129886/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdPdYQxvMuynpX7iW__JNLTby6EV5TxAqskZKBRqjlv8pUyTnn-A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T03:50:13.433921962Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aSlRIWnFXVUZCTlVWbWRYSldNbHBTVkZKME0wRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aSlRIWnFXVUZCTlVWbWRYSldNbHBTVkZKME0wRRAB!2m1!1s0x80deaba33f943573:0x21b30dc0f2d3b05c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25abk5HWnZiWFpXY0RCbU1FMW5SRE5OUVZGM01HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "We got the Oaxaca California burrito. Which is a very generous portion of meat inside. Very flavorful. Absolutely bang for your buck. It’s definitely worth it. I ate 1/3 and had the rest for the next day.\nDon’t forget to tip!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We got the Oaxaca California burrito. Which is a very generous portion of meat inside. Very flavorful. Absolutely bang for your buck. It’s definitely worth it. I ate 1/3 and had the rest for the next day.\nDon’t forget to tip!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Marie B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114498478672103435651/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWphItNXViLZC5S9C5QrJF9fnL-l56f_w67WLiE_06fXbeYtBg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-06T12:22:53.223712880Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25abk5HWnZiWFpXY0RCbU1FMW5SRE5OUVZGM01HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25abk5HWnZiWFpXY0RCbU1FMW5SRE5OUVZGM01HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80deaba33f943573:0x21b30dc0f2d3b05c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRFFVMVpOMHRyVTFWbFRYRkZUWE5uZFcxMmIzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Great tasting Cali Burrito. The meat is very well seasoned. I added sour cream and held back on the pico. It was a great tasting burrito, not quite the best, but very good. They are tightly wrapped, but they are not as large as others that also taste great. For $14.49 it could be bigger. The staff was very friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great tasting Cali Burrito. The meat is very well seasoned. I added sour cream and held back on the pico. It was a great tasting burrito, not quite the best, but very good. They are tightly wrapped, but they are not as large as others that also taste great. For $14.49 it could be bigger. The staff was very friendly.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Xavier B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104779775947758943073/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrJHSO7y9KmqSJ1_4LN_uisY0I_s503pNIOi0f5s36lC-JHQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-31T04:36:39.447875676Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRFFVMVpOMHRyVTFWbFRYRkZUWE5uZFcxMmIzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2sxRFFVMVpOMHRyVTFWbFRYRkZUWE5uZFcxMmIzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80deaba33f943573:0x21b30dc0f2d3b05c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGeE5UaHpPVzh5YmxaVE1GQmxVVGRRYURJelVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Best surf and turf burritos I’ve had in sd! Everything tasted fresh. Great salsas too. Friendly service, busy long wait, limited seating, call ahead of time for pickup. My partner loves their oxacalifornia burrito too", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Best surf and turf burritos I’ve had in sd! Everything tasted fresh. Great salsas too. Friendly service, busy long wait, limited seating, call ahead of time for pickup. My partner loves their oxacalifornia burrito too", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Molly T", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103539585500730437789/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWp0WpcM2Q6g5EGiKVVN30RGH_e3k6ndEW-CKts6Sk5YXmmBoM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-13T18:45:20.114294221Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGeE5UaHpPVzh5YmxaVE1GQmxVVGRRYURJelVsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGeE5UaHpPVzh5YmxaVE1GQmxVVGRRYURJelVsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80deaba33f943573:0x21b30dc0f2d3b05c"}, {"name": "places/ChIJczWUP6Or3oARXLDT8sANsyE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aV01sZGtRM1JRY0UxMllYVmxYMEY1TTFWaFZIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This place is an absolute gem and everyone should pay a visit at least once when visiting San Diego. Family-owned, authentic Mexican restaurant that serves amazing food. I went there with my celiac girlfriend and they were able to accomodate her with some incredible options. Absolutely reccommended for people with gluten allergy too.\n\nCarne Asada Burrito: nothing to say, try it. It was spectacular.\nNachos & Guacamole (gluten free): amazing taste, guacamole was great.\nAl Pastor Taco (gluten free): try it, it's amazing.\nEnchilladas with queso (gluten free): 10 out of 10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This place is an absolute gem and everyone should pay a visit at least once when visiting San Diego. Family-owned, authentic Mexican restaurant that serves amazing food. I went there with my celiac girlfriend and they were able to accomodate her with some incredible options. Absolutely reccommended for people with gluten allergy too.\n\nCarne Asada Burrito: nothing to say, try it. It was spectacular.\nNachos & Guacamole (gluten free): amazing taste, guacamole was great.\nAl Pastor Taco (gluten free): try it, it's amazing.\nEnchilladas with queso (gluten free): 10 out of 10.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Massimo Ingrande", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105240342687360631000/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYUrAnXe3eaJIHjfAiMtJ9AA0pj7hKeqZCp8ddRr3rFNMrwQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": 